---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { socialLinks } from "../config";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---
<Base>
  <section>
    <a href={socialLinks.twitter} target="_blank">
      <Image
        src="/profile.png"
        alt="Profile photo"
        class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 block lg:mt-5 mt-0 lg:mb-5 mb-10 mx-auto sm:float-right sm:ml-5 sm:mb-5 grayscale hover:grayscale-0"
        width={200}
        height={200}
      />
    </a>
    
    <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert">
      <h4 class="mb-4 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Reading</h4>
      <p>I regularly alternate between papers and whole texts. My most recent read was Mirjam Tuk's <a href="https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=1720956&">paper on urgency control and decision-making</a>.</p>
      
      <h4 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Writing</h4>
      <p>I write about various topics of interest. Here are a few of my favourites:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://t18e.com/blog/discontent">Discontent</a>: on the implications of our relationship with social media.</li>
        <li><a href="https://t18e.com/blog/cide-effects">Cide Effects</a>: on the language surrounding suicide stigma.</li>
        <li><a href="https://t18e.com/blog/yeah-write">Yeah, Write</a>: on writing without LLMs as a form of agency.</li>
        <li><a href="https://t18e.com/blog/african-intelligence">African Intelligence</a>: on the commercialisation of Afrobeats.</li>
        <li><a href="https://t18e.com/blog/say-my-name">Say My Name</a>: on product names & word-of-mouth growth.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h4 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Products</h4>
      <p>Here are a few tools I'm loving:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://en.app/" target="_blank">En</a>: the search engine for books.</li>
        <li><a href="https://docsend.com/" target="_blank">DocSend</a>: for document tracking.</li>
        <li><a href="https://twist.com/" target="_blank">Twist</a>: for async team communication.</li>
        <li><a href="https://consensus.app/" target="_blank">Consensus</a>: for intelligent academic research.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h4 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Research Interests</h4>
      <p>I'm currently interested in: digital dualism, sociolinguistics, omnichain infrastructure, cryptocurrency policy, the shadow gig economy, and the right to self-determination.</p>
      
      <h4 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Other</h4>
      <p><a href="https://justgiving.com/page/tiwa">I recently campaigned</a> for the <a href="https://autistica.org.uk/">UK's leading autism research and advocacy charity</a>. <a href="https://t18e.com/blog/autistica">Here's why</a> I supported Autistica.</p>
      
      <h4 class="mb-4 mt-8 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Contact</h4>
      <p>Reach out via <a href="mailto:mail@t18e.com?subject=Reaching%20out%20from%20your%20website&body=Hi%20Tiwa,%0A%0AReaching%20out%20from%20your%20website.">email</a> or <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/tiwa-adejuyigbe">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
